{"tid":2322869,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"防彈少年團三度奪大賞！舞台告白A.R.M.Y：永遠留在我身邊","createTime":"2020-12-12T16:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T16:31:07.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e11979bbfa43fc72a3f218a6d283bdefc26a43db","tid":2322869,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:29:54.000Z","msg":"南韓音樂盛典「The Fact Music Awards」（TMA）12日晚間7點在首爾舉行，因應疫情，紅毯和演出皆採取事先錄製的方式，但頒獎仍是歌手們現場領取。防彈少年團再度拿下「大賞」，這也是他們第三次拿到該典禮的大賞，他們更在演出時於佈景感性向粉絲A.R.M.Y告白：「留在我身邊。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5330/d5330971.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5330%2Fd5330971.jpg&h=2033970e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團第三度拿下「The Fact Music Awards」大賞。（圖／翻攝自播出畫面）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5330/d5330974.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5330%2Fd5330974.jpg&h=68d3996a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n防彈少年團除了第三度拿下大賞外，更囊括「Listeners's Choice」、「TMA人氣獎」和「2020年度藝人獎」，四獎入袋是當晚的大贏家。隊長RM在得到大賞後，感性表示：「我們何德何能，能夠代替各位以激動的心情獲得這個大獎呢？在無法舉行公演的情況下，依然竭盡全力努力製作音樂的所有音樂人們，我想把這個獎的榮耀送還給你們。」<br />\n<br />\n他們也帶來包括《Dynamite》和《Life Goes On》兩首歌曲演出，在開頭的VCR更對粉絲告白：「留在我身邊，永遠留下來，我的人生都是關於你。」儘管成員SUGA正在手術恢復期未能出席，BTS沒忘記帶著他的人形立牌，更俏皮的擺出一樣的姿勢合照。"},{"pid":"e86870ecf656978f218353f409091b0533db3ad1","tid":2322869,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"垃圾不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee585b37a9f385a6760180b1779887a72b9f080","tid":2322869,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5331/d5331001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5331%2Fd5331001.jpg&h=fe6fc58e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁唔老黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24fd30a4a089cd66a7423e6760b33ceb1bc3aa3","tid":2322869,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e86870ecf656978f218353f409091b0533db3ad1","tid":2322869,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"垃圾不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:31:07.000Z","msg":"問號問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}